                          <span>致谢</span>
                          <span
                            class="text-[10px] font-normal text-on-surface-variant/50 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors animate-pulse"
                          >
                            (点击展开/折叠)
                          </span>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant/80">本项目学习/参考了部分以下开源项目的内容。</p>
                      </div>
                      <ChevronDownIcon
                        class="w-4 h-4 text-on-surface-variant transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:text-primary"
                        :class="{ 'rotate-180': showAcknowledgements }"
                      />
                    </div>

                    <!-- 折叠展开的内容区域 -->
                    <div
                      class="grid transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
